You cannot include clicky-nukes in the balancing discussion, because a casting class should be balanced <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> without</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> equipment.  Also, not every wizard has a conflag robe, and not every druid has their clicky items.<br>
