<br>
One more thing (to make sure there is no misunderstanding):<br>
<br>
I really am not saying that druids need to be nerfed, or that they are really &quot;overpowered&quot;.  They are really only &quot;overpowered&quot; when you look at what wizards <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> are</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, instead of what wizards <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> should be</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br>
